# Backend Middleware Module

## PURPOSE
Express middleware for authentication, validation, and error handling.
Reusable middleware functions for request processing.

## CONTAINS
- auth.js: JWT authentication middleware
- validate.js: Request validation middleware
- errorHandler.js: Global error handler
- rateLimiter.js: Rate limiting middleware

## AUTH MIDDLEWARE
- verifyToken(): Validate JWT token from Authorization header
- requireAuth(): Ensure user is authenticated
- requirePaid(): Ensure user has paid for premium access

## VALIDATION MIDDLEWARE
- validateRegister(): Validate registration data
- validateLogin(): Validate login credentials
- validatePayment(): Validate payment data

## ERROR HANDLER
- Catch all errors from routes
- Return consistent error format
- Log errors for debugging
- Hide sensitive info in production

## REFERENCES
- Parent: /backend/.windsurf
- Root: /.windsurf
- Used by: /backend/routes/*

## RULES
- Always validate JWT signature
- Return 401 for authentication failures
- Return 403 for authorization failures
- Return 400 for validation errors
- Log all authentication attempts
- Implement rate limiting on auth routes
